# ── Dependencies (Phase 2-A, Session #18) ──────────────────────────────
# The published site is dependency-free Vanilla JS. node_modules is only the
# local install of the pinned dev tools (eslint/stylelint/playwright/http-server).
# It is reproducible from package-lock.json via `npm ci` and must never be committed.
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# ── Python bytecode caches ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated by running the .github/scripts/*.py checkers locally. Not source.
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# ── Playwright local artifacts (baselines are produced/committed via CI) ──
/test-results/
/playwright-report/
/blob-report/
/playwright/.cache/

# ── OS / editor noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
